com.ephesoft.dcma.kvfieldcreation

Class KVFieldCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.kvfieldcreation.KVFieldCreator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommonConstants

    @Component
@Scope(value="prototype")
public class KVFieldCreator
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICommonConstants
    This class creates the key value field in batch class for every document level field of each document in the batch. New object is needed for each request of method of this class.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
    See Also:
    KVFieldCreatorService
